 comfort.", "text": "Enjoy the most soothing and relaxing atmosphere by staying in one of the 15 rooms. Spaces designed for those who want to live a truly special experience without giving up maximum comfort."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/5", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "section_header", "prov": [{"page_no": 1, "bbox": {"l": 11.54547503893852, "t": 503.667767254596, "r": 109.73448423182607, "b": 490.26551800130426, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 10]}], "orig": "RESTAURANT", "text": "RESTAURANT", "level": 1}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/6", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 1, "bbox": {"l": 11.54547503893852, "t": 477.0132039696745, "r": 370.01540661976605, "b": 410.55953093742556, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 232]}], "orig": "Join us for an unforgettable culinary journey in a truly stunning setting. Savor our daily Kenyan dishes with authentic flavors, or indulge in our exquisite international menu, thoughtfully curated from our travels around the world.", "text": "Join us for an unforgettable culinary journey in a truly stunning setting. Savor our daily Kenyan dishes with authentic flavors, or indulge in our exquisite international menu, thoughtfully curated from our travels around the world."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/7", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "section_header", "prov": [{"page_no": 1, "bbox": {"l": 10.731024752873951, "t": 383.67331383232835, "r": 197.89925143296378, "b": 380.9727765872443, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 22]}], "orig": "MALINDI ARTISAN MARKET", "text": "MALINDI ARTISAN MARKET", "level": 1}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/8", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 1, "bbox": {"l": 11.54547503893852, "t": 363.1618863134796, "r": 272.0250402563147, "b": 296.70821328123066,